data.subject: Turpentine
data.lyric:
I watch you grow away from me in photographs
 And memories like spies
 And salt betrays my eyes agai

data.subject: The Story
data.lyric:
All of these lines across my face
 Tell you the story of who I am
 So many stories of where I've bee

data.subject: Late Morning Lullaby
data.lyric:
As soon as my eyes shut the slide show begins
 Yesterday is gone now and panic sets in
 With a weigh
